<%- include('../partials/head', { title: 'Simulated Global Investing' }) %>
<%- include('../partials/nav') %>
<%- include('../partials/disclaimer') %>
<main id="main">
  <%- include('../partials/flash') %>

  <section class="hero hero-legendary container">
    <div class="hero-copy">
      <p class="eyebrow">Simulated forex, macro and portfolio command center</p>
      <h1>Train inside a private capital desk without risking a single real dollar.</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        USF Capital is a premium software demo for simulated investing. It blends a live FX-style ticker,
        virtual portfolio allocation, risk controls, security workflows and a ticking performance engine into one
        cinematic investor portal. No real funds, no real brokerage activity, no hidden payment flow.
      </p>

      <div class="hero-metrics" aria-label="Platform highlights">
        <div>
          <span class="metric-value <%= heroStat.avgReturnPct >= 0 ? 'positive' : 'negative' %>">
            <%= heroStat.avgReturnPct >= 0 ? '+' : '' %><%= (heroStat.avgReturnPct * 100).toFixed(1) %>%
          </span>
          <span class="metric-label">avg. simulated pool growth, <%= heroStat.days %> days</span>
        </div>
        <div>
          <span class="metric-value">$<%= totalCapDollars.toLocaleString('en-US', { maximumFractionDigits: 0 }) %></span>
          <span class="metric-label">virtual lifetime deposit cap</span>
        </div>
        <div>
          <span class="metric-value"><%= lockYears %>Y</span>
          <span class="metric-label">simulated position lock cycle</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="/register" class="btn btn-primary btn-large">Enter the Demo Desk</a>
        <a href="/how-it-works" class="btn btn-secondary btn-large">View the Engine</a>
      </div>
      <p class="fine-print hero-note">Built as a portfolio-grade demo. Every price, return, balance and chart is simulated.</p>
    </div>

    <aside class="hero-terminal card" aria-label="Live simulated market ticker">
      <div class="terminal-topline">
        <span class="terminal-dot"></span>
        <span class="terminal-dot"></span>
        <span class="terminal-dot"></span>
        <span>USF // MARKET PULSE</span>
      </div>
      <h2 class="card-title">Live Simulated Market Snapshot</h2>
      <ul id="ticker-list" class="ticker-list ticker-list-legendary">
        <li class="ticker-placeholder">Loading simulated prices&hellip;</li>
      </ul>
      <div class="terminal-grid" aria-label="Illustrative desk controls">
        <span>Spread Watch</span><strong>Armed</strong>
        <span>Risk Gate</span><strong>Online</strong>
        <span>Ledger Mode</span><strong>Demo</strong>
      </div>
      <p class="fine-print">Illustrative FX/index prices, automatically refreshed. Not real market data.</p>
    </aside>
  </section>

  <section class="container desk-strip" aria-label="Capital desk modules">
    <article class="desk-card">
      <span class="desk-icon">FX</span>
      <h2>Global Macro &amp; FX</h2>
      <p>Simulated exposure to major pairs, currency momentum and macro-style drift.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="desk-card">
      <span class="desk-icon">RISK</span>
      <h2>Capital Guardrails</h2>
      <p>Deposit caps, lock cycles, penalty math and route-level limiters keep the demo disciplined.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="desk-card">
      <span class="desk-icon">VAULT</span>
      <h2>Security Theater, But Real Code</h2>
      <p>CSRF tokens, bcrypt, session storage, 2FA setup and strict headers are actual app protections.</p>
    </article>
  </section>

  <section class="container market-board-section">
    <div class="section-heading section-heading-row">
      <div>
        <p class="eyebrow">Performance laboratory</p>
        <h2>Four simulated pools, one command chart</h2>
        <p>This chart is generated by the same simulation engine that powers investor dashboards.</p>
      </div>
      <a href="/pools" class="btn btn-ghost btn-small">Explore Pools</a>
    </div>
    <div class="card chart-card market-board">
      <canvas id="home-pools-chart" data-chart-type="multiline" height="360" role="img"
        aria-label="Simulated index performance for four investment pools over the last 180 days" tabindex="0"></canvas>
      <script type="application/json" id="home-pools-chart-data"><%- JSON.stringify({
        formatValue: 'index',
        series: seriesByPool.map(({ pool, series }) => ({
          label: pool.name,
          color: pool.color,
          points: series.map(p => ({ ts: p.ts, value: p.index_value }))
        }))
      }) %></script>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="container strategy-grid-section">
    <div class="section-heading">
      <p class="eyebrow">Inside the machine</p>
      <h2>More than a static landing page</h2>
      <p>USF Capital behaves like a miniature fintech system: account flows, portfolio math, audit-style messaging and live UI feedback.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="strategy-grid">
      <article class="strategy-card">
        <span class="strategy-number">01</span>
        <h3>Virtual funding flow</h3>
        <p>Mock card, bank and crypto deposit choices let users experience onboarding without payment collection.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="strategy-card">
        <span class="strategy-number">02</span>
        <h3>Pool allocation engine</h3>
        <p>Users split simulated cash across equity growth, global macro/FX, fixed income and digital assets.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="strategy-card">
        <span class="strategy-number">03</span>
        <h3>Live portfolio ticking</h3>
        <p>Positions evolve through a backend simulation loop locally and request-driven catch-up on serverless deploys.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="strategy-card">
        <span class="strategy-number">04</span>
        <h3>Security cockpit</h3>
        <p>Sessions, activity logs, CSRF checks, rate limits and optional authenticator-app 2FA make the demo credible.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="container trust-strip legendary-trust" aria-label="Illustrative trust badges">
    <div class="trust-badge">
      <strong>Hardened Headers</strong>
      <span>Helmet CSP, frame denial, browser policy headers and no-store rules for private routes.</span>
    </div>
    <div class="trust-badge">
      <strong>Simulated Audit Trail</strong>
      <span>Security-relevant activity is logged for the account owner to review.</span>
    </div>
    <div class="trust-badge">
      <strong>Demo KYC Flow</strong>
      <span>A guided identity check demonstrates onboarding without external verification.</span>
    </div>
    <p class="fine-print">These are demo features and software-design examples. USF Capital is not a licensed or regulated financial institution.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="container cta-band cta-legendary">
    <p class="eyebrow">Open the vault door</p>
    <h2>Launch the simulated desk and test the full investor journey.</h2>
    <p>Create a free simulated account in under a minute. No payment details are ever required.</p>
    <a href="/register" class="btn btn-primary btn-large">Open a Free Simulated Account</a>
  </section>
</main>
<%- include('../partials/footer') %>
<script src="/js/ticker.js"></script>
<script src="/js/charts.js"></script>
